<P align=left>Lastly a reminder that Winter is here and all those expensive Winter School items such as blazers, woollen jumpers and even footwear needs labelling . For the price of 22.00 for 60&nbsp;ironons can you afford to lose any more school gear. Try our permanent ironon range for a great easy to apply and highly durable product that Parents schools and kids love..and dont forget our shoe labels for those change of seasons and sports too! Check out our <A title="clothing labels" href="http://www.identikid.com.au/Products/Clothing_Labels">clothing label range here</A></P>
<P>And why not make some money for the school by getting a fundraiser code and brochures organised. identikids NO fuss fundraising takes the work out of fundraising. Simply go to our website to <A title="fundraising registration" href="http://www.identikid.com.au/Fundraisers">register</A> or get a info pack . Fundraisers can make up to 15-25% on all products ordered.</P>
<P>To unsubscribe to any further newsletters click&nbsp; <A href="mailto:info@identikid.com.au">info@identikid.com.au</A>&nbsp;and request removal from loyalty program and email database. Your email will be removed from all future mailouts. Currently we expect 4 newsletters a year. </P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE><A href="http://www.identikid.com.au/content.php?page=235"></A></TD>
